reviews.review_text: Where are the reviews? Was at this show and the following night.  I thought these were some of the best MSG shows I saw.  This night the end of the first set and the second set through stella blue are wonderful.  Check out the jam coming out of Weather Report with Jerry and Bruce. Thanks for the posting as this is hard to find.  Recording is great !
